::Perndabot/FZ::

Perndabot's eyes narrow, his muscles getting ready to send him at 
Biomass. He calculates his jump and a few slashes afterward, about to 
release when..

"Perndabot, stand down."

Perndabot's muscles relax, the robot turning around to see FZ 
standing outside the shuttles that had just landed.

"What's going on here?" FZ asks, approaching the two bots and looking 
them over.
